lead_paragraph: The Terrapins got 17 points each from two players in a victory over the visiting Hawkeyes, who lost in their first game since climbing to No. 3, their highest ranking since 1987.

headline.print_headline: No. 8 Maryland Ends a Nine-Game Run by No. 3 Iowa
